track_notes: This is the track from Mt. Le Conte Shelter to Myrtle Point which has great views in addition to being a good operating point that is within the AZ
This trail starts from between Sugarlands and Gatlinburg near Fighting Creek Gap Road on Newfound Gap Road US441
This track goes from parking for the Alum Cave Bluff Trail on Hwy 441 directly to the summit of Mount Le Conte, skipping Le Conte Lodge, the shelter, and viewpoints.
track_title: Our track to Mount Le Conte summit via Alum Cave Bluff Trail
